{{data.airports}}</p>

</div>

<div class='about_mnt_size'>
  <p>Acres: {{data.acres}} </p>
  <p>Number of Trails: {{data.num_trails}}</p>
  <p>Number of Lifts: {{data.num_lifts}}</p>
</div>


